         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melb. Botan. Garden ¶ 21/6/70 ¶  ¶ Let me thank you, dear Mr Moule, for your prompt attention to the wishes of the Trustees, to advise them professionally in reference to the financial irregularities ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.06.21b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Frederick Moule</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A345 Royal Park Zoological Society letter &amp; minute book, p. 38, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melb. Botan. Garden</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">21/6/70</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me thank you, dear Mr Moule, for your prompt attention to the wishes of the Trustees, to advise them professionally in reference to the financial irregularities in Lissignol's administration of the Royal Park.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">get details from minutes.</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">E. Lissignol was the Acclimatisation Society ranger at Royal Park. He was appointed to a French Consular post in Bombay. The Society's routine audit uncovered an embezzlement of £100,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">Lissignol was arrested on the day of his departure, but the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">arrest<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">warrant was cancelled by the Police Magistrate when a friend repaid the money</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">;</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Lissignol left for<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">India on 22 May 1879 (</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #043FFF; ">Age</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Melbourne), 24 May 1870, p. 2</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #043FFF; ">. Further investigation revealed a much larger fraud. See M to J. MacPherson, 18 July 1870, which enclosed a report by Moule and another by the auditor.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I will place your legal report before my colleagues at an early meeting probably to be held already on Friday next.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Your regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Fred. Moule Esq.</p>
